HEADWORD: Holophotal
<hw>Hol`o*pho"tal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Holo</ets>
+ Gr. <?/, <?/, light.]</ety> <fld>(Opt.)</fld> <def>Causing no loss of
